text: Le Grand-Saconnex is a municipality in the canton of Geneva in Switzerland. Geneva International Airport is partially within the borders of Le Grand- Saconnex. == Twin town == Le Grand Saconnex is twinned with:Conseil des Communes et Regions d'Europe accessed 27 April 2011 * Carantec in Brittany, France == References == == Other websites == * Grand-Saconnex Category:Municipalities of Geneva Category:Cities in Switzerland
